  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%;
  background: transparent; transition: background 0.3s;
  padding: 10px 0; z-index: 1000;
}
nav ul {
  list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 0; padding: 0;
